item.title: CVE-2017-20013|2024-06-06T16:12:44.207Z -- weka -- interest%20security%20scanner
item.description: A vulnerability classified as problematic was found in WEKA INTEREST Security Scanner up to 1.8. Affected by this vulnerability is the Stresstest Configuration Handler. A manipulation leads to a local denial of service. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used. NOTE: This vulnerability only affects products that are no longer supported by the maintainer
